## Terraform Lifecycle:

- terraform init = (Initialize the Terraform configuration. Providers plugin download module load, Backend Load)
- terraform plan = (Blueprint of infra after apply)
- terraform apply = (apply the terraform configuration)
- terraform apply --auto-approve = This option is used to bypass.
- terraform destroy = (delete the terraform configuration)
- terraform workspace = tf workspace list 
- tf workspace = show = To show workspace of terraform
- tf workspace list = To show the workspace list of Terraform 
- terraform --var-file=vars/dev.tfvar = For Variable 
- terraform workspace select dev = to Change the environment.
- terraform destroy - To destroy 
- terraform --replace="aws_instance.my-instance" - To replace the instance replace 
- terraform apply --refresh-only = to refresh the environment of the infrastructure
